title: Final Fantasy: Tactics A2 - Grimoire of the Rift (Europe - Austr
description:
Purchased from a Australian retail store, somehow before release. Hooray for breaking release dates. Full game, (seems to, tested for about 20 minutes) work using most recent R4DS firmware.

Has English, Spanish, French and German language options. No box scans because I&#039;m lazy, and want to sleep.

Compressed using 7z (www.7-zip.org), 128MB when extracted.  Enjoy.
